  "html": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"2025-13\">2025-13</h2>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"daily-check-in--reflections\">Daily Check-In &#x26; Reflections</h3>\n<!-- Note any physical activity, mindfulness practice, or self-care -->\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"-learning--media\">📚 Learning &#x26; Media</h3>\n<!-- Books, articles, movies, TV shows, podcasts consumed -->\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/FCk8sicNMDo?si=_EjJQi0NijzO7SkK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://youtu.be/FCk8sicNMDo?si=_EjJQi0NijzO7SkK\">https://youtu.be/FCk8sicNMDo?si=_EjJQi0NijzO7SkK</a></p>\n<p class=\"\">I have been really enjoying watching Ludwig and Michael Reaves travel across Japan.</p>\n<p class=\"\">Michael Reaves himself is a worthwhile rabbit hole, and I found after watching one of his videos I had to watch him all, and I found the energy and momentum and creativity extremely inspirational.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Clustering algorithm comparisons using UMAP visualization: HDBSCAN with varying min_cluster_size and min_samples parameters versus KMeans with 8-25 clusters on gene expression data.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742920633/Screenshot_2025-03-25_at_12.37.00_PM.png\" alt=\"Clustering algorithm comparisons using UMAP visualization: HDBSCAN with varying min_cluster_size and min_samples parameters versus KMeans with 8-25 clusters on gene expression data.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1742920633/Screenshot_2025-03-25_at_12.37.00_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1742920633/Screenshot_2025-03-25_at_12.37.00_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742920633/Screenshot_2025-03-25_at_12.37.00_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1742920633/Screenshot_2025-03-25_at_12.37.00_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Clustering algorithm comparisons using UMAP visualization: HDBSCAN with varying min_cluster_size and min_samples parameters versus KMeans with 8-25 clusters on gene expression data.\" width=\"1650\" height=\"1620\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.06deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1650×1620\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-square w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Clustering algorithm comparisons using UMAP visualization: HDBSCAN with varying min_cluster_size and min_samples parameters versus KMeans with 8-25 clusters on gene expression data.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742920786/Screen_Recording_2025-03-25_at_12.38.58_PM.mov\" alt=\"Screenshot - 2025-03-25 12:39 - Screen Recording 2025-03-25 at 12.38.58 PM.mov\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1742920786/Screen_Recording_2025-03-25_at_12.38.58_PM.mov 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1742920786/Screen_Recording_2025-03-25_at_12.38.58_PM.mov 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1742920786/Screen_Recording_2025-03-25_at_12.38.58_PM.mov 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/video/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1742920786/Screen_Recording_2025-03-25_at_12.38.58_PM.mov 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.74deg;\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"UMAP dimensionality reduction plot showing s